title: Deepika Padukone, Ranbir Kapoor feasted on French delicacies while in Corsica
text: Deepika Padukone, Ranbir Kapoor feasted on French delicacies while in Corsica Saturday, 24 October 2015 (4 minutes ago) Young stars Deepika Padukone and Ranbir Kapoor feasted on French delicacies while filming in Corsica for their upcoming film 'Tamasha'.
